09:36.710 --> 09:39.880
Like a death-row prisoner
granted a reprieve

09:39.947 --> 09:42.950
at the 11th hour,
Childrens Hospital

09:43.016 --> 09:45.118
lives to see another day.

09:45.185 --> 09:48.255
Only, this show won't spend it's
first day of freedom getting

09:48.321 --> 09:49.823
